title: Biden Proposes $6 Trillion Budget to Boost Middle Class and Infrastructure
description: President Biden proposed a $6 trillion budget on Friday that would increase spending to fuel economic growth and help America better compete with China.

title: Israeli Airstrikes Kill Dozens in Gaza as Tensions Escalate
description: Israel launched a wave of airstrikes in Gaza on Sunday, killing dozens of people and injuring hundreds, as tensions between Israel and Hamas continued to escalate.

title: Elon Musk Tweets Support for Dogecoin, Sending Price Soaring
description: Elon Musk tweeted his support for Dogecoin on Thursday, sending the cryptocurrency's price soaring by more than 20%.
